{"tid":1407283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位睇緊Live嘅連登仔，其實我想解釋下「手段」同「目的」","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:06:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T02:16:15.000Z","uid":53803,"like":122,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2ff032caf968b4218247087e5da6137902c854a0","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"希望各位可以聽我講幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實每次遊行，一到入夜，<br />\n就會多咗好多指責post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C13Nf3z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC13Nf3z.png&h=de488923&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eRLzFvf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeRLzFvf.png&h=66f64b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pYNf3A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pYNf3A.png&h=01c682e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為一個廿幾歲年輕人，<br />\n其實每次上完前線翻黎睇到啲指責post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好失士氣，見到好多正評甚至覺得被割蓆<br />\n但係我好明白一樣野，唔計三毛，<br />\n大部分人（上年紀嘅人）都係咁諗野：<br />\n<br />\n「要有個目的，然後去用手段去達成」<br />\n例如612，立法會要開會，<br />\n所以衝擊係係為咗阻止佢開會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係一但唔係根據呢個邏輯，<br />\n就會有人出黎（上左年紀嘅人）指責：<br />\n「其實有乜目的？做乜乜乜仲好啦」<br />\n例如71衝立會，其實連登當晚都係指責多<br />\n覺得「又冇人係裡面，衝黎做乜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有同前線嘅學生討論過，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實而家大部分年青人都係呢個邏輯<br />\n「我嘅目的，就係我嘅手段」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有呢種諗法原因係源於政府無視，<br />\n冷處理所有和理非遊行，<br />\n無論你做乜，<br />\n都見唔到有任何手段係達成到目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而大家最終都係想有五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以好多示威者（年輕果批）都覺得要整啲野<br />\n俾政府睇到，「我地升級緊行動，請你盡快處理」<br />\n<br />\n所以問題就係到：<br />\n點解要縱火？因為要縱火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解要塞紅隧？因為要塞紅隧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解要衝立會？因為要衝立會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人大個左，好多野都要計成本效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n諗下點先可以最快達成到目的<br />\n但而家其實好多人諗法都轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得要搞啲野出黎<br />\n俾人睇到年青人有不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地可以做嘅，就係盡量理解班學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以作千萬個理由去目的化佢地嘅行動<br />\n符合翻自己嘅思考方式<br />\n但不妨理解下佢地嘅思考方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾多啲意見，唔好成日指責<br />\n記住我地係同一路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文太長，預左冇乜人睇，盡量推下post<br />\n有緣人即管看看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時化革命"},{"pid":"9ad0beaea01f2694e19789d0f02b365af406b03e","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:08:11.000Z","msg":"得閒睇下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65c91335120c8935a7ae5fb62b0e420d64b645b","tid":1407283,"uid":45914,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1ea2c18e250d29bdbe1a89321c7a48f828cc717","tid":1407283,"uid":38332,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"做乜執晒劉細良口水尾"},{"pid":"c2ad6cc121df161b1ffd3b6b8c346346011cdd6e","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"d65c91335120c8935a7ae5fb62b0e420d64b645b","tid":1407283,"uid":45914,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"有改善空間你可以提出<br />\n唔好用啲指責嘅口敏<br />\n「冇用」「又消耗民意」<br />\n老實講句示威就係要有影響<br />\n<br />\n如果你係上左年紀嘅人<br />\n我真係明你嘅思維，<br />\n覺得要有針對 有目的<br />\n但你可以了解佢地燒野就係佢地個目的<br />\n咪試下理解囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e926559625edf26e0c9df8a589210cdb3b9df0","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"c1ea2c18e250d29bdbe1a89321c7a48f828cc717","tid":1407283,"uid":38332,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"做乜執晒劉細良口水尾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"有聽過佢講，我覺得可以再用文字宣傳下<br />\n唔想次次都係指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd9eaba681aefc43428eb89d21b68ff4bc61073","tid":1407283,"uid":33939,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"本身我都覺要目的，但自從留守立法會嘅死士，同自殺嘅人出現。我就知道啲人係寧願犧牲都要持續住哩個運動。<br />\n<br />\n當然，我都唔希望示威者有死傷或俾人拉。"},{"pid":"670f2f21452c0b708525b2c3fdeeff79efaaed4b","tid":1407283,"uid":264626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"我之前都係你講個D和理非咁諗。<br />\n<br />\n不過後來改變左，因為如果每一步都如政府計算之中咁，呢場運動一早 game over ，政府就係一味唔回應，想好似當年雨傘咁令民心漸失，我地唔可以令暴政得逞。<br />\n<br />\n我只求前線小心，唔好傷害到自己同無辜市民，其他任何所謂民生，阻人返工個D，根本到左今日，支持個批人唔會介意，唔支持個D，做乜都屌。<br />\n<br />\n不過最好逐步升級，比D時間大多數人去適應每次既升級，唔好一下子去到太激"},{"pid":"b19eb83140a95e7fa60dcf77481fedf6f54f0572","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bd9eaba681aefc43428eb89d21b68ff4bc61073","tid":1407283,"uid":33939,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"本身我都覺要目的，但自從留守立法會嘅死士，同自殺嘅人出現。我就知道啲人係寧願犧牲都要持續住哩個運動。<br />\n<br />\n當然，我都唔希望示威者有死傷或俾人拉。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"係 其實睇得耐都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地諗野係好單純"},{"pid":"892934fcee9d3609465b045a65cd3b094c1ba7be","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"670f2f21452c0b708525b2c3fdeeff79efaaed4b","tid":1407283,"uid":264626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"我之前都係你講個D和理非咁諗。<br />\n<br />\n不過後來改變左，因為如果每一步都如政府計算之中咁，呢場運動一早 game over ，政府就係一味唔回應，想好似當年雨傘咁令民心漸失，我地唔可以令暴政得逞。<br />\n<br />\n我只求前線小心，唔好傷害到自己同無辜市民，其他任何所謂民生，阻人返工個D，根本到左今日，支持個批人唔會介意，唔支持個D，做乜都屌。<br />\n<br />\n不過最好逐步升級，比D時間大多數人去適應每次既升級，唔好一下子去到太激"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:17:55.000Z","msg":"其實唔單止和理非<br />\n前線果啲有時都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48248d9737e1c0e2a6ba6193755379229bfb911c","tid":1407283,"uid":45914,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c652ba521080d14111457764f2728da279dbd423","tid":1407283,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36af3933de0195c34732f11b6774d45c3e56573c","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"48248d9737e1c0e2a6ba6193755379229bfb911c","tid":1407283,"uid":45914,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c2ad6cc121df161b1ffd3b6b8c346346011cdd6e","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"d65c91335120c8935a7ae5fb62b0e420d64b645b","tid":1407283,"uid":45914,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"有改善空間你可以提出<br />\n唔好用啲指責嘅口敏<br />\n「冇用」「又消耗民意」<br />\n老實講句示威就係要有影響<br />\n<br />\n如果你係上左年紀嘅人<br />\n我真係明你嘅思維，<br />\n覺得要有針對 有目的<br />\n但你可以了解佢地燒野就係佢地個目的<br />\n咪試下理解囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:22:36.000Z","msg":"你問題第一句，<br />\n都仲係用緊一個目的手段嘅思考方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n燒野嘅目的係燒野<br />\n塞隧道嘅目的係塞隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為已經沒有對準政權嘅事可做<br />\n圍政總警總律政司禮賓府真係冇試過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地只可以用呢啲方式去宣洩不滿"},{"pid":"aa2acdc07f2a1e3f9d70aa42f9f3610615e880e1","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c652ba521080d14111457764f2728da279dbd423","tid":1407283,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:23:47.000Z","msg":"你可以咁諗 係令到群眾有更多attention係呢件事上<br />\n亦都俾政府有更多attention係呢件事上"},{"pid":"def01953d29a3c22d52c760a66a0117a4cd2cd87","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"唉 俾啲包容啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e63ca626b57da3cfe71fc499b391e3d2d7322b","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:26:37.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"a2bc0fb03b8a5fc97fc7415147b4515d6ddc9e8b","tid":1407283,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dec6bd1b031881d5306c1bf0702f2e31b7c307ff","tid":1407283,"uid":31974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"呢場運動正正就係有咁多不確定因素<br />\n咁多不確定既行動<br />\n我地先可以行到呢一步<br />\n<br />\n都係個句 做乜都唔割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6995751c54ed586db982b8463b4d47174961bde3","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2bc0fb03b8a5fc97fc7415147b4515d6ddc9e8b","tid":1407283,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"def01953d29a3c22d52c760a66a0117a4cd2cd87","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:24:52.000Z","msg":"唉 俾啲包容啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:26:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"叫你係同路人就包容啲前線<br />\n你唔係嘅就死開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9fe16887f73c31048c1ec11057f85673541905","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dec6bd1b031881d5306c1bf0702f2e31b7c307ff","tid":1407283,"uid":31974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"呢場運動正正就係有咁多不確定因素<br />\n咁多不確定既行動<br />\n我地先可以行到呢一步<br />\n<br />\n都係個句 做乜都唔割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"唔好割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少啲指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多啲善意意見"},{"pid":"a12f6cfaeffb60fa3c2cf866d3a174161a05d39a","tid":1407283,"uid":103653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"次次做完野都問佢地做黎做乜尻<br />\n我真係想問開Pos