 />\n少啲指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多啲善意意見"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:33:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8bca3830a9be07fd1627b62ad84934f9ff93e2","tid":1407283,"uid":32502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"大佬呀<br />\n你估共產黨d維穩費流既咩<br />\n呢d自己判斷<br />\n<br />\n核彈都唔會話1句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f4bdb43e09411879f4f55d1a0b497db21de329","tid":1407283,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"- 游擊戰為主，路障戰，陷阱戰，遠攻戰，3方配合游擊戰<br />\n- 與警狗保持長距離防線，防止狗突然衝擊，可以安全退後。<br />\n- 短期防守，絕不長期守。<br />\n- 如果見到警狗開始佈防，就要立即全部人轉場地，令佢地on99咁浪費時間<br />\n- 如果沒有辦法反擊畜龍或水車，不要等待畜龍或水車出現先退後。一見到佢地身影，設路障或陷阱後就立即退後。<br />\n- 絕不硬頸，不能硬碰，更不要企硬對峙。<br />\n- 不留戀任何戰線地點，要流水式打擊，打擊完就去下一個目標。<br />\n- 聽同伴意見，不被捕為主。"},{"pid":"da49f8a371f42b7b9e73b3682ce34cfbf4a7355d","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f8bca3830a9be07fd1627b62ad84934f9ff93e2","tid":1407283,"uid":32502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"大佬呀<br />\n你估共產黨d維穩費流既咩<br />\n呢d自己判斷<br />\n<br />\n核彈都唔會話1句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"除左毛軍，其實我知有好多上左年紀<br />\n出左社會嘅人都會有呢個思考方式<br />\n我只希望佢地可以理解下前線"},{"pid":"baad9d0cf6ad57e1ca6abb251e2251409d5a3d3f","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85f4bdb43e09411879f4f55d1a0b497db21de329","tid":1407283,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"- 游擊戰為主，路障戰，陷阱戰，遠攻戰，3方配合游擊戰<br />\n- 與警狗保持長距離防線，防止狗突然衝擊，可以安全退後。<br />\n- 短期防守，絕不長期守。<br />\n- 如果見到警狗開始佈防，就要立即全部人轉場地，令佢地on99咁浪費時間<br />\n- 如果沒有辦法反擊畜龍或水車，不要等待畜龍或水車出現先退後。一見到佢地身影，設路障或陷阱後就立即退後。<br />\n- 絕不硬頸，不能硬碰，更不要企硬對峙。<br />\n- 不留戀任何戰線地點，要流水式打擊，打擊完就去下一個目標。<br />\n- 聽同伴意見，不被捕為主。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72f8e5f5c95d21063edfca749f12564e604f700","tid":1407283,"uid":250586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"我唯一會屌只係死勸都唔肯走嗰啲，至於手段=目的，我是認同的"},{"pid":"adbc1f71907390f37801c0fd0b0a0997eb5707cd","tid":1407283,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:37:53.000Z","msg":"支持巴打你<br />\n<br />\n支持為香港付出既人<br />\n<br />\n香港加油！"},{"pid":"9e354ac6a9ff74a30bb5ab55cef337ed3fdb7ad3","tid":1407283,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:37:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f308a9f9aa3507d1220e7e1c90eba808644a737","tid":1407283,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"Yes 唔該大家恢復理性<br />\n劉細良同梁天琦都禁講<br />\n唔好比仇恨蓋過理性"},{"pid":"d8f4357ce386ba7c34bc71af6e74ccd571d64d0c","tid":1407283,"uid":257366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ff032caf968b4218247087e5da6137902c854a0","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"希望各位可以聽我講幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實每次遊行，一到入夜，<br />\n就會多咗好多指責post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C13Nf3z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC13Nf3z.png&h=de488923&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eRLzFvf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeRLzFvf.png&h=66f64b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pYNf3A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pYNf3A.png&h=01c682e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為一個廿幾歲年輕人，<br />\n其實每次上完前線翻黎睇到啲指責post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好失士氣，見到好多正評甚至覺得被割蓆<br />\n但係我好明白一樣野，唔計三毛，<br />\n大部分人（上年紀嘅人）都係咁諗野：<br />\n<br />\n「要有個目的，然後去用手段去達成」<br />\n例如612，立法會要開會，<br />\n所以衝擊係係為咗阻止佢開會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係一但唔係根據呢個邏輯，<br />\n就會有人出黎（上左年紀嘅人）指責：<br />\n「其實有乜目的？做乜乜乜仲好啦」<br />\n例如71衝立會，其實連登當晚都係指責多<br />\n覺得「又冇人係裡面，衝黎做乜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有同前線嘅學生討論過，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實而家大部分年青人都係呢個邏輯<br />\n「我嘅目的，就係我嘅手段」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實有呢種諗法原因係源於政府無視，<br />\n冷處理所有和理非遊行，<br />\n無論你做乜，<br />\n都見唔到有任何手段係達成到目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而大家最終都係想有五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以好多示威者（年輕果批）都覺得要整啲野<br />\n俾政府睇到，「我地升級緊行動，請你盡快處理」<br />\n<br />\n所以問題就係到：<br />\n點解要縱火？因為要縱火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解要塞紅隧？因為要塞紅隧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解要衝立會？因為要衝立會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人大個左，好多野都要計成本效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n諗下點先可以最快達成到目的<br />\n但而家其實好多人諗法都轉左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得要搞啲野出黎<br />\n俾人睇到年青人有不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地可以做嘅，就係盡量理解班學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以作千萬個理由去目的化佢地嘅行動<br />\n符合翻自己嘅思考方式<br />\n但不妨理解下佢地嘅思考方式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾多啲意見，唔好成日指責<br />\n記住我地係同一路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文太長，預左冇乜人睇，盡量推下post<br />\n有緣人即管看看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時化革命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"你喺空曠地方玩火，我覺得情有可原<br />\n但如果用火波及到附近民居，傷害無辜市民，我絕對唔可以接受"},{"pid":"e5610482a553501f59723ba9ab9c5257c3b60add","tid":1407283,"uid":81518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:41:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8136fe672de0bc5fea1238fa2c55a7ab840de771","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"如果整到民居<br />\n我同你地道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但希望大家明白政府冷處理<br />\n咩都唔做先有今日呢啲情況"},{"pid":"c1cd5ba2cfab65092d1f169ff76a5fb3864445d7","tid":1407283,"uid":53803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69285f915d67492f2bc832ac203e69a4582fc8e7","tid":1407283,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:43:30.000Z","msg":"8月5日，全民三罷！<br />\n<br />\n遍地開花 九巴不合作運動最後召集！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406002</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n所有最新資訊會係TG Group到發放，有意發夢參加的朋友請加入<br />\n<br />\n已有分區細group，入谷後pm admin<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=wovbC19maxltJNBkbBY4lIc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D